dalam sunda = senen kemis
dalam indonesia = senin kamis
dalam deutsch = montag Donnerstag(google translate jujur we abi mah)
in english

1. read this du'a
"niat abdi puasa poe senen (monday) or kemis (thursday) karena Allah ta'ala"
2. do sahur one hour before imsak (you can search it, if you don't know what is imsak :) )
3. and do puasa till maghrib
4. doneee you have completed puasa senen/kemis
